          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1203.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Peel and chop the <strong>brown&nbsp;onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Once the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> are browned, reduce the heat to&nbsp;medium-low</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until softened&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1203.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1203.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1203.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1203.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1203.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and slice the <strong>parsnips</strong> into thin disks&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Strip the <strong>rosemary</strong> and <strong>thyme leaves</strong> and chop finely, discarding the stems</p>\r\n<p>Dissolve the <strong>chicken stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[35</span><span class=\"text-danger\">0ml]&nbsp;</span><strong>boiled water&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1203.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1203.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1203.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1203.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1203.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Increase the heat to medium, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>rosemary</strong> and <strong>thyme</strong> and cook for 1 min</p>\r\n<p>Add the<strong> chicken stock</strong> and <strong>sliced parsnips</strong> and cook, covered, for 6-7 min&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
