            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate the<strong>&nbsp;cheddar&nbsp;cheese&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Combine the<strong> panko breadcrumbs</strong> and <strong>grated cheese</strong> with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once done, transfer the <strong>chicken</strong> to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks &ndash; this technique is known as &lsquo;pulling&rsquo;</p>\r\n<p>Return the <strong>shredded chicken</strong> and the<strong> sour cream</strong> to the pan and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper&nbsp;</strong></p>",
